{"tid":1686713,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦想1月引入迪姆華拿","createTime":"2019-11-01T10:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T13:19:27.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d69f1f0bfddbe9a27137b3a1645e63995e37f78","tid":1686713,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"利物浦打算在前線增兵，目標是1月出手買RB萊比錫的德甲前鋒迪姆華拿。<br />\n<br />\n迪姆華拿一直盛傳是紅軍獵物，現在有消息指球會想1月買人。但為了增加成事機會，他們願意買人之後將他會回萊比錫完成下半季，不急於今季要人。<br />\n<br />\n華拿今季上陣14場入10球及交出3次助攻，表現受人注目，曼聯也都有意思搶人強化前鋒線。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=5082d37d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"5bcccd8c60d4bb5196db3ab395872a9b2e9988ab","tid":1686713,"uid":221419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:15:31.000Z","msg":"力子夠做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bdc4a0805dc627323933b37c4444564bc942d9","tid":1686713,"uid":134623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d69f1f0bfddbe9a27137b3a1645e63995e37f78","tid":1686713,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"利物浦打算在前線增兵，目標是1月出手買RB萊比錫的德甲前鋒迪姆華拿。<br />\n<br />\n迪姆華拿一直盛傳是紅軍獵物，現在有消息指球會想1月買人。但為了增加成事機會，他們願意買人之後將他會回萊比錫完成下半季，不急於今季要人。<br />\n<br />\n華拿今季上陣14場入10球及交出3次助攻，表現受人注目，曼聯也都有意思搶人強化前鋒線。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=5082d37d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"食撚左次借返一年先來基達水貨仲未夠？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b34a5766520181ad14021ac4997bae0693f8c0","tid":1686713,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"條友好似多人睇佢踢波<br />\n會緊張到嘔 傻佬黎喎"},{"pid":"44a9f096b